Back to King’s 2023

  • 14 August, 2023
  • Short Videos

Thank you for joining us at Back to King’s 2023.

It was a beautiful day as the Old Boy’s Union, Family and Friends Association and families of King’s came together to show their support and reminisce. As King’s played against St Joseph’s College on home soil, it was wonderful to witness our community come together and enjoy the King’s spirit.

Congratulations to each of our teams for their determination and dedication to their sport, and thank you to everyone who came to watch, cheer and encourage our boys.

We hope you enjoy this video from the day.
